summary: Places a house inside Riverwood! It\'s actually inside the walls, behind the Inn.
descriptionHtml:
This is my first take at modding, so feedback is encouraged. 

This mod is NOT compatible with Forested Riverwood. At least not without deleting/moving some of the stuff that is behind the Inn..

Cell beneath house isn\'t quite finished yet. I will update this as soon as i figure out how to code with Papryus and find something cool to put down there.

The house has a complete smithing area, enchantment table, and alchemy bench. and none of the containers respawn so you can store everything safely!
author: Rodger Walker
